272
00:20:09.842 --> 00:20:13.010
Someone is strategically placing these boxes.

273
00:20:13.012 --> 00:20:18.182
We have to find out who
and why before it's too late.

274
00:20:27.725 --> 00:20:31.061
Desaad. what do you have to report

275
00:20:31.063 --> 00:20:32.329
From our agents on Earth?

276
00:20:32.331 --> 00:20:36.600
Sire. the powerful one
has found a mother box.

277
00:20:36.602 --> 00:20:41.171
The one they mistakenly call Superman.

278
00:20:41.706 --> 00:20:42.739
And?

279
00:20:42.741 --> 00:20:45.142
These defenders have
sprung up like antibodies

280
00:20:45.144 --> 00:20:48.645
To protect their planet.
We are in danger of losing

281
00:20:48.647 --> 00:20:50.380
The element of surprise. my lord.

282
00:20:50.382 --> 00:20:54.584
I humbly ask that you move up your timetable.

283
00:20:55.720 --> 00:20:58.388
Let the invasion begin.

284
00:21:01.159 --> 00:21:03.493
We're maxed at power ceiling.

285
00:21:03.495 --> 00:21:05.262
Cycle the pulses.

286
00:21:07.765 --> 00:21:10.134
Dr. Stone... your son is here.

287
00:21:10.135 --> 00:21:13.637
- I don't have time right now.
- Do it again.

288
00:21:13.638 --> 00:21:14.655
Make time.

289
00:21:14.706 --> 00:21:18.141
Victor. I'm in the middle
of some very important work.

290
00:21:18.143 --> 00:21:20.444
You mean more important than me.

291
00:21:20.446 --> 00:21:22.679
That's not what I said.

292
00:21:22.681 --> 00:21:25.215
There were scouts there today. dad.

293
00:21:25.217 --> 00:21:28.251
They offered me a full ride. all of them.

294
00:21:28.253 --> 00:21:30.253
I told you I'll pay for college.

295
00:21:30.255 --> 00:21:32.689
You don't need to be sniffing
after a scholarship.

296
00:21:32.691 --> 00:21:33.723
That's not the point.

297
00:21:33.725 --> 00:21:38.662
They think I can hold my own
with the best of the best.

298
00:21:38.664 --> 00:21:40.464
Why don't you?

299
00:21:40.466 --> 00:21:42.165
Open your eyes. son.

300
00:21:42.167 --> 00:21:44.167
Look at the world we live in today.

301
00:21:44.169 --> 00:21:47.671
We are witnessing the birth
of a new race of Superhumans.

302
00:21:47.673 --> 00:21:51.509
Beings who can fly. tear through buildings.
and outrun race cars.

303
00:21:51.510 --> 00:21:54.444
They will make what you can do obsolete.

304
00:21:54.446 --> 00:21:58.882
In that world.
throwing a football is a joke.

305
00:21:59.650 --> 00:22:03.420
You're never gonna come
to one of my games. are you?

306
00:22:05.591 --> 00:22:06.591
No.

307
00:22:06.592 --> 00:22:09.126
Dr. Stone. something's happening.

308
00:22:09.128 --> 00:22:11.862
We can talk about this later.

309
00:22:17.034 --> 00:22:20.604
So why are you two here?
Metropolis is my turf.

310
00:22:21.506 --> 00:22:25.706
There have been reports of mysterious
kidnappings across the country.

311
00:22:25.743 --> 00:22:28.862
We had 'em here. too.
Figured that was life in the big city.

312
00:22:28.914 --> 00:22:31.715
You think the disappearances
and these things are connected?

313
00:22:31.717 --> 00:22:33.150
They're connected.

314
00:22:33.152 --> 00:22:34.618
So these monsters. they're...

315
00:22:34.620 --> 00:22:37.420
they're soldiers.
expendable soldiers at that.

316
00:22:37.422 --> 00:22:39.856
Planting these devices at all costs.

317
00:22:39.858 --> 00:22:40.858
That's military tactics.

318
00:22:40.859 --> 00:22:43.493
We might be staring down the barrel

319
00:22:43.495 --> 00:22:44.828
Of a full-Scale invasion.

320
00:22:44.829 --> 00:22:46.013
You're paranoid.

321
00:22:46.064 --> 00:22:49.733
Let's just crack it open
and see what happens.

322
00:22:49.734 --> 00:22:50.768
Hey!

323
00:22:50.769 --> 00:22:52.903
Without any idea what's inside?

324
00:22:52.905 --> 00:22:54.538
That's idiotic.

325
00:22:54.540 --> 00:22:57.207
Heh. I'll show you idiotic.

326
00:22:58.510 --> 00:23:00.277
Ahh! I didn't touch it.

327
00:23:00.279 --> 00:23:02.412
It's activated itself.

328
00:23:02.414 --> 00:23:03.647
It's transmitting.

329
00:23:03.649 --> 00:23:05.282
Silas. look at these readings.

330
00:23:05.284 --> 00:23:09.620
I am not letting you walk away from me again.
dad. We're having this out.

331
00:23:09.621 --> 00:23:10.854
Can we trace the power source?

332
00:23:10.856 --> 00:23:13.957
I'm trying to lock in on the signal now.

333
00:23:14.225 --> 00:23:16.860
This thing is more important to you

334
00:23:16.862 --> 00:23:18.428
Than your own son?

335
00:23:18.430 --> 00:23:20.263
Victor. stop!

336
00:23:23.334 --> 00:23:25.869
It's gonna blow!

337
00:23:30.943 --> 00:23:32.609
Aah!

338
00:24:02.540 --> 00:24:04.741
You're welcome.

339
00:24:25.363 --> 00:24:27.764
Still think I'm paranoid?

340
00:24:27.766 --> 00:24:30.900
Ah. maybe a little less now.

341
00:25:00.064 --> 00:25:02.767
- We need to get out of here now.
- Which way?

342
00:25:02.768 --> 00:25:06.436
We have to get him into the red room.

343
00:25:22.853 --> 00:25:24.354
Sarah!

344
00:25:40.037 --> 00:25:42.605
I'm not leaving you. Victor.

345
00:25:42.607 --> 00:25:45.342
Don't you dare leave me.

346
00:25:54.786 --> 00:25:55.786
I don't believe it.

347
00:25:55.787 --> 00:25:59.089
His vitals are there. Silas. He's alive.

348
00:26:04.696 --> 00:26:05.696
Dad.

349
00:26:05.697 --> 00:26:07.597
Yes. Victor. I'm here.

350
00:26:07.599 --> 00:26:10.433
Ahh. It hurts so bad.

351
00:26:10.435 --> 00:26:11.534
It's going to hurt.

352
00:26:11.536 --> 00:26:14.070
It's not gonna be easy. but...

353
00:26:15.607 --> 00:26:16.607
Whatever that energy is.

354
00:26:16.608 --> 00:26:18.808
It's eating him from the inside out.

355
00:26:18.810 --> 00:26:21.444
He's going into cardiac arrest.

356
00:26:21.446 --> 00:26:23.880
It's racing up his spinal cord.

357
00:26:23.882 --> 00:26:25.949
Then we can't wait.

358
00:26:31.523 --> 00:26:32.789
But. Silas. the risk.

359
00:26:32.791 --> 00:26:34.023
What choice so I have. morrow?

360
00:26:34.025 --> 00:26:36.726
This room contains technology
recovered from across the globe.

361
00:26:36.728 --> 00:26:39.062
I've studied and logged
nearly everything in here.

362
00:26:39.064 --> 00:26:41.664
I've taken apart and rebuilt most of it.

363
00:26:41.666 --> 00:26:44.000
It can save my son's life.

364
00:26:44.002 --> 00:26:45.568
It has to.

365
00:27:05.189 --> 00:27:07.724
- He's in pain.
- You have to do something.

366
00:27:07.726 --> 00:27:10.460
The pain will subside
as soon as the promethium

367
00:27:10.462 --> 00:27:12.028
Finishes replacing the damaged tissue.

368
00:27:12.030 --> 00:27:13.496
Promethium skin grafts?

369
00:27:13.498 --> 00:27:15.932
His body could reject them completely.

370
00:27:15.933 --> 00:27:18.768
It won't. I've injected the nanites.
Activate them.

371
00:27:18.770 --> 00:27:21.438
- They're untested.
- We recovered them from...

372
00:27:21.440 --> 00:27:23.072
Do it!

373
00:27:29.980 --> 00:27:31.648
Aah!

374
00:27:56.842 --> 00:28:00.009
Out of the way. you freaky bimbo!

375
00:28:00.011 --> 00:28:02.946
Cool. You're Wonder Woman.

376
00:28:02.948 --> 00:28:05.081
My name is Diana.

377
00:28:05.083 --> 00:28:06.950
Mine's Hannah grace.

378
00:28:06.952 --> 00:28:09.652
Thank you for speaking with me. Hannah.

379
00:28:09.654 --> 00:28:10.954
You're not afraid of me.

380
00:28:10.956 --> 00:28:14.157
Nah. I wanna be you when I get big.

381
00:28:14.159 --> 00:28:17.527
I would welcome your sisterhood. Hannah.

382
00:28:17.529 --> 00:28:18.928
What are you eating?

383
00:28:18.930 --> 00:28:20.964
Ice cream.

384
00:28:21.199 --> 00:28:22.199
Is it good?

385
00:28:22.200 --> 00:28:25.134
It's the greatest food in the world.

386
00:28:25.136 --> 00:28:27.270
If you ask me.

387
00:28:28.639 --> 00:28:29.906
Aww.

388
00:28:30.508 --> 00:28:32.675
I will try some ice cream.

389
00:28:32.677 --> 00:28:36.145
And another for my friend Hannah.

390
00:28:36.648 --> 00:28:37.648
Whatever you say. lady.

391
00:28:37.649 --> 00:28:41.751
Just don't. you know. take my arm with it.

392
00:28:41.753 --> 00:28:43.786
Eh. here.

393
00:28:48.726 --> 00:28:51.895
Ice cream is wonderful!

394
00:28:53.030 --> 00:28:55.031
Told you so.

395
00:28:55.666 --> 00:28:59.536
You should be very proud of this achievement.

396
00:28:59.538 --> 00:29:02.205
Um. thanks?

397
00:29:05.243 --> 00:29:07.243
I lost him.

398
00:29:07.245 --> 00:29:10.747
I promised his mother I'd protect him.

399
00:29:10.749 --> 00:29:13.149
But I failed.

400
00:29:16.720 --> 00:29:18.655
What's going on?

401
00:29:38.175 --> 00:29:39.709
Diana.

402
00:29:39.877 --> 00:29:42.946
Steve. have you ever had ice cream?

403
00:29:42.948 --> 00:29:46.082
This cook is truly blessed.

404
00:29:46.084 --> 00:29:48.851
You need to come back to the white house.

405
00:29:48.852 --> 00:29:49.887
You sound like my mother.

406
00:29:49.888 --> 00:29:52.288
The President only has
a few minutes to meet you.

407
00:29:52.290 --> 00:29:55.692
I grew weary of waiting for him. so I left.

408
00:29:55.694 --> 00:29:57.126
This is Hannah.

409
00:29:57.128 --> 00:29:59.095
Very pleased to meet you.

410
00:29:59.097 --> 00:30:01.364
Could you excuse us. Hannah?

411
00:30:01.366 --> 00:30:04.067
You can't walk out like that. Diana.

412
00:30:04.069 --> 00:30:05.735
You're a political envoy.

413
00:30:05.737 --> 00:30:08.304
I am a warrior.

414
00:30:08.306 --> 00:30:10.273
With responsibilities.

415
00:30:10.275 --> 00:30:14.844
Besides. I happen to know where they make
the best homemade ice cream in D.C..

416
00:30:14.845 --> 00:30:16.196
If you're interested.

417
00:30:17.047 --> 00:30:20.683
Oh. I could compel you
to disclose this secret.

418
00:30:20.685 --> 00:30:23.853
Or I could just take you there.

419
00:30:34.231 --> 00:30:37.200
There is my true responsibility.

420
00:30:37.202 --> 00:30:41.170
Combat. Leave them to me.

421
00:31:13.971 --> 00:31:16.406
Upload initiated.

422
00:31:16.408 --> 00:31:17.740
Completed.

423
00:31:17.742 --> 00:31:19.308
Recalibrating memory.

424
00:31:22.279 --> 00:31:24.914
What's happening?

425
00:31:24.916 --> 00:31:26.182
Stay calm. son.

426
00:31:26.184 --> 00:31:28.017
It's gonna be all right.

427
00:31:33.824 --> 00:31:36.926
- Hey. dr. Stone. I...
- We're in trouble!

428
00:32:09.126 --> 00:32:11.494
Offensive mode activated.

429
00:32:35.085 --> 00:32:37.220
Aah!

430
00:33:20.164 --> 00:33:21.964
Victor!

431
00:33:26.303 --> 00:33:28.905
I came as quick as I could.

432
00:33:28.907 --> 00:33:33.109
Offensive mode... White noise cannon enabled.

433
00:34:06.476 --> 00:34:08.477
Lantern. plug that hole.

434
00:34:08.479 --> 00:34:11.113
Yeah. yeah. I got this.

435
00:34:25.262 --> 00:34:26.562
Concentrate.

436
00:34:26.564 --> 00:34:28.631
Your constructs are fading.

437
00:34:28.633 --> 00:34:30.366
Your mind is scattered.

438
00:34:30.368 --> 00:34:31.868
Worry about yourself.

439
00:34:31.870 --> 00:34:34.403
You're the one without powers.

440
00:34:35.572 --> 00:34:37.940
We need to take a step back and regroup.

441
00:34:37.942 --> 00:34:41.244
There's too many of them
just to barrel through.

442
00:34:41.246 --> 00:34:42.578
Yeah?

443
00:34:44.481 --> 00:34:47.516
Tell that to Superman. Ohh!

444
00:34:54.324 --> 00:34:55.958
Come on.

445
00:34:56.360 --> 00:34:57.526
That's it.

446
00:34:57.528 --> 00:34:59.662
Smile for me.

447
00:35:09.306 --> 00:35:13.676
- Mayday. Mayday.
- The capital is under attack.

448
00:35:16.179 --> 00:35:19.015
And there goes our big gun.

449
00:35:19.017 --> 00:35:21.417
Fantãstico.

450
00:35:31.128 --> 00:35:33.095
Aw. come on.

451
00:35:33.964 --> 00:35:36.465
Can't a guy get any privacy?

452
00:35:36.467 --> 00:35:38.267
Football. Told you so.

453
00:35:38.269 --> 00:35:39.669
Well. we had to be certain.

454
00:35:39.671 --> 00:35:42.638
I was so worried about you. Billy.

455
00:35:42.640 --> 00:35:45.708
- You don't have to be.
- For real.

456
00:35:45.710 --> 00:35:47.343
I like your jersey.

457
00:35:47.345 --> 00:35:48.711
Oh. yeah? I stole it.

458
00:35:48.713 --> 00:35:50.980
You did not. You're funny.

459
00:35:50.982 --> 00:35:53.382
We worry every time you disappear.

460
00:35:53.384 --> 00:35:56.619
You know. like a family would.

461
00:35:56.621 --> 00:35:59.155
Foster family.

462
00:36:01.458 --> 00:36:03.259
This time was the worst.

463
00:36:03.261 --> 00:36:06.395
You've heard the reports. right?

464
00:36:07.631 --> 00:36:09.732
There's an invasion of monsters.

465
00:36:09.734 --> 00:36:13.202
They're grabbing people off the streets.

466
00:36:14.472 --> 00:36:18.074
And you morons believe that?

467
00:36:20.110 --> 00:36:21.744
Jerk.

468
00:36:40.031 --> 00:36:42.264
Come and get some. ugly.

469
00:36:42.266 --> 00:36:43.766
Shazam!

470
00:37:09.226 --> 00:37:12.194
They're being overcautious. hon.

471
00:37:12.196 --> 00:37:14.497
We'll be fine.

472
00:37:20.670 --> 00:37:23.606
I need eyes up. pronto.

473
00:37:36.486 --> 00:37:37.486
We're under siege.

474
00:37:37.488 --> 00:37:41.157
Repeat. the president is under siege.

475
00:37:42.559 --> 00:37:43.826
Aah!

476
00:37:59.509 --> 00:38:00.676
Mr. President.

477
00:38:00.678 --> 00:38:03.312
It's nice to finally meet you.

478
00:38:03.314 --> 00:38:06.148
I am Diana. But you may call me...

479
00:38:06.150 --> 00:38:09.118
Wonder woman. Thank goodness.

480
00:38:42.352 --> 00:38:44.753
We've lost an engine!

481
00:38:46.556 --> 00:38:48.524
Julian!

482
00:38:48.526 --> 00:38:50.559
Aah!

483
00:39:10.147 --> 00:39:13.516
Are we ok? What's going on?

484
00:39:15.585 --> 00:39:18.587
By the gods.

485
00:39:29.599 --> 00:39:31.200
You're strong.

486
00:39:31.202 --> 00:39:33.702
I know.

487
00:39:41.845 --> 00:39:43.812
Can't feel my hand.

488
00:39:43.814 --> 00:39:46.315
Can't feel anything.

489
00:39:47.684 --> 00:39:49.818
What's happened to me?

490
00:39:50.921 --> 00:39:54.857
Your mind is now a quantum computer. son.

491
00:39:54.859 --> 00:39:57.293
There's buzzing in my ears.

492
00:39:57.295 --> 00:39:59.695
Make it stop. please.

493
00:39:59.696 --> 00:40:02.531
I can't.
At least you're alive.

494
00:40:02.533 --> 00:40:05.501
Uhh. You call this living.

495
00:40:05.503 --> 00:40:08.404
this half-Man. half-Machine?

496
00:40:08.406 --> 00:40:11.740
This is what it took for you
to finally care about me?

497
00:40:11.742 --> 00:40:16.312
You had to make me just
another one of your experiments.

498
00:40:17.414 --> 00:40:20.382
Don't you hear the buzzing?

499
00:40:22.352 --> 00:40:25.254
- You know what?
- I think I am needed downtown.

500
00:40:25.256 --> 00:40:29.491
And you two clearly
need to talk. so I'll just.

501
00:40:29.493 --> 00:40:32.361
Uh... Yeah.

502
00:40:41.838 --> 00:40:43.839
Unassimilated data detected.

503
00:40:43.841 --> 00:40:46.842
Commencing parademon indoctrination.

504
00:40:46.844 --> 00:40:49.712
Download initiated.

505
00:40:55.385 --> 00:40:57.253
Translating. Command...

506
00:40:57.255 --> 00:40:59.855
Locate inhabitable worlds.

507
00:41:07.031 --> 00:41:11.000
Command... Harvest organic material.

508
00:41:14.838 --> 00:41:18.641
Command... Process organic material.

509
00:41:20.010 --> 00:41:23.979
Command... Repurpose organic material.

510
00:41:40.930 --> 00:41:42.831
Command...

511
00:41:42.833 --> 00:41:44.867
for Darkseid.

512
00:41:58.682 --> 00:42:00.049
Download complete.

513
00:42:05.989 --> 00:42:07.690
Darkseid.

514
00:42:23.740 --> 00:42:25.941
Excuse me. but this is the hole

515
00:42:25.943 --> 00:42:29.478
These wigglers crawled out of. right?

516
00:42:30.580 --> 00:42:32.614
Vic stone?

517
00:42:32.616 --> 00:42:35.517
What the hell happened to you?

518
00:43:02.946 --> 00:43:04.747
That wasn't so hard.

519
00:43:13.390 --> 00:43:15.758
Looks like you could use a hand.

520
00:43:15.760 --> 00:43:17.059
Flash! My boy.

521
00:43:17.061 --> 00:43:19.094
Great to see you.

522
00:43:22.832 --> 00:43:24.767
Oh. yeah. and that's Batman.

523
00:43:24.769 --> 00:43:26.068
Batman's real?

524
00:43:26.070 --> 00:43:27.803
Yeah. He's over there.

525
00:43:27.804 --> 00:43:28.738
Wait. What?

526
00:43:28.739 --> 00:43:32.708
It is a real honor to meet you. sir. Batman.

527
00:43:32.710 --> 00:43:33.976
Sir ba... Batman. sir.

528
00:43:33.978 --> 00:43:36.111
- Don't bother.
- The guy's a total tool.

529
00:43:36.113 --> 00:43:39.548
I've followed your efforts
in central city. Flash.

530
00:43:39.550 --> 00:43:42.551
You do tight. efficient work.

531
00:43:42.819 --> 00:43:47.723
Hey. Barry. you. uh. got
a little something on your nose.

532
00:43:48.458 --> 00:43:50.826
Get ready. Here they come.

533
00:43:50.828 --> 00:43:53.796
For Darkseid!

534
00:43:56.533 --> 00:43:58.167
Hah!

535
00:44:08.711 --> 00:44:10.446
Holy...

536
00:44:25.929 --> 00:44:28.597
Greetings. warriors.

537
00:44:29.165 --> 00:44:31.767
Dibs.

538
00:44:31.769 --> 00:44:33.902
Hi.

539
00:44:35.638 --> 00:44:38.907
Ah. it's good to be back in the heat of war.

540
00:44:38.909 --> 00:44:42.144
Yeah. you better run.

541
00:44:42.146 --> 00:44:43.545
No. they're assembling.

542
00:44:43.547 --> 00:44:47.616
Waiting for whoever's behind
this to launch the attack.

543
00:44:47.618 --> 00:44:48.951
All right. Now what?

544
00:44:48.953 --> 00:44:51.220
I don't know.

545
00:44:55.024 --> 00:44:56.625
Incoming!

546
00:45:01.097 --> 00:45:02.631
Mine.

547
00:45:03.566 --> 00:45:06.502
Defense mode activated.

548
00:45:07.938 --> 00:45:08.938
Damn it.

549
00:45:08.939 --> 00:45:10.072
You're done.

550
00:45:10.074 --> 00:45:12.274
No! I'm not with them!

551
00:45:12.276 --> 00:45:16.612
- Hold on. I can vouch for that.
- He was at S.T.A.R. Labs.

552
00:45:18.582 --> 00:45:19.882
Huh?

553
00:45:26.823 --> 00:45:28.690
Hey there. What's up?

554
00:45:28.692 --> 00:45:30.826
Shazam.

555
00:45:30.828 --> 00:45:32.528
I'm with him.

556
00:45:32.530 --> 00:45:34.763
He's not with me.

557
00:45:34.765 --> 00:45:38.835
And who the hell are you supposed to be.
Mr. Roboto?

558
00:45:38.836 --> 00:45:43.205
- Who I am doesn't matter.
- What I know does.

559
00:45:43.206 --> 00:45:44.173
Which is?

560
00:45:44.174 --> 00:45:45.174
I've...

561
00:45:45.175 --> 00:45:48.277
talked to their technology.

562
00:45:48.279 --> 00:45:49.311
I know their plan.

563
00:45:49.313 --> 00:45:52.047
They're terraforming the Earth.

564
00:45:52.049 --> 00:45:54.850
It's about to get ugly.

565
00:45:54.852 --> 00:45:57.252
- That fits.
- How do you figure?

566
00:45:57.254 --> 00:45:59.054
Well. for one thing.

567
00:45:59.056 --> 00:46:01.657
The water's on fire.

568
00:46:29.285 --> 00:46:31.086
What are they doing with them?

569
00:46:31.088 --> 00:46:32.921
Can't be sure. but I know this.

570
00:46:32.923 --> 00:46:36.224
They're not killing anyone.
They're harvesting them.

571
00:46:36.226 --> 00:46:38.093
This isn't an isolated incident either.

572
00:46:38.095 --> 00:46:40.729
It's happening across the world.

573
00:46:47.270 --> 00:46:51.106
We're too late. He's here.

574
00:47:02.919 --> 00:47:05.287
I'm guessing that's the bad guy.

575
00:47:05.288 --> 00:47:06.368
Lucky guess.

576
00:47:06.456 --> 00:47:09.124
He doesn't look that tough.

577
00:47:25.408 --> 00:47:26.408
No.

578
00:47:27.077 --> 00:47:29.277
I am entropy.

579
00:47:29.279 --> 00:47:32.180
I am death.

580
00:47:37.820 --> 00:47:40.656
I am Darkseid.

581
00:47:40.658 --> 00:47:43.325
Stand back and peep the light show.

582
00:47:43.327 --> 00:47:46.662
Green Lantern's got this.

583
00:48:07.684 --> 00:48:09.017
That all you got?

584
00:48:09.019 --> 00:48:10.185
Not all I got.

585
00:48:21.164 --> 00:48:24.766
Uhh. I'm not through with you.

586
00:48:26.969 --> 00:48:30.072
Aah!

587
00:48:45.221 --> 00:48:47.322
Is that your boyfriend?

588
00:48:47.324 --> 00:48:49.157
No.

589
00:48:49.159 --> 00:48:50.992
Cool. Watch this.

590
00:48:50.994 --> 00:48:52.227
Hey. blackheart the deatheater

591
00:48:52.229 --> 00:48:55.163
or whatever your
"World of Warcraft" name is...

592
00:48:55.165 --> 00:48:56.798
Suck on this!

593
00:49:05.742 --> 00:49:06.875
Now what?

594
00:49:06.877 --> 00:49:09.845
Now you die.

595
00:49:13.015 --> 00:49:14.883
Wait! No!

596
00:49:28.531 --> 00:49:30.398
We're gonna have to move fast.

597
00:49:30.400 --> 00:49:32.467
Not a problem for me.

598
00:49:35.037 --> 00:49:37.339
- They're splitting up.
- They can do that?

599
00:49:37.341 --> 00:49:39.307
- They're locked on us.
- Come on. Barry.

600
00:49:39.309 --> 00:49:42.043
You're moving fast. so think fast.

601
00:49:57.794 --> 00:50:01.897
Whew. Never had to catch my breath before.

602
00:50:01.899 --> 00:50:04.499
Oh. no. Superman.

603
00:50:17.046 --> 00:50:20.816
Finally. the kryptonian is ours.

604
00:50:20.818 --> 00:50:23.919
Master will be pleased.

605
00:50:33.462 --> 00:50:37.833
- They flew off with him.
- I saw it. They took Superman.

606
00:50:38.267 --> 00:50:39.501
I'll get him.

607
00:50:39.503 --> 00:50:41.469
Lantern!

608
00:50:46.543 --> 00:50:47.909
Out of my way. Batman.

609
00:50:47.911 --> 00:50:50.512
Your arm is broken. you idiot.

610
00:50:51.280 --> 00:50:55.383
- I can handle this.
- Get out of my way.

611
00:50:55.451 --> 00:50:57.586
- You're gonna die.
- Then I die.

612
00:50:57.588 --> 00:50:59.120
What are you trying to prove?

613
00:50:59.122 --> 00:51:01.523
I'm not trying to prove anything.

614
00:51:01.525 --> 00:51:03.491
You phenomenal douche bag.

615
00:51:03.493 --> 00:51:07.462
Don't act like you know me. You don't.

616
00:51:08.097 --> 00:51:10.932
We're just somewhat alike.

617
00:51:10.934 --> 00:51:12.334
We are nothing alike.

618
00:51:12.336 --> 00:51:14.402
We're fighting alongside an alien. an Amazon.

619
00:51:14.404 --> 00:51:17.405
A human lightning bolt.
a cyborg. and a speedster.

620
00:51:17.407 --> 00:51:19.941
Far as I can tell. Hal. you and I

621
00:51:19.943 --> 00:51:21.443
Are the only normal people here.

622
00:51:21.445 --> 00:51:24.412
I never told you my name.

623
00:51:24.414 --> 00:51:26.147
Saw it on your flight suit.

624
00:51:26.149 --> 00:51:29.885
You're pretty south of normal. spooky.

625
00:51:29.887 --> 00:51:32.120
You know that. right?

626
00:51:32.222 --> 00:51:33.222
My name is Bruce Wayne.

627
00:51:33.223 --> 00:51:37.259
When I was 10. my parents were
murdered in front of my eyes.

628
00:51:37.261 --> 00:51:39.027
I've spent my life training to fight

629
00:51:39.029 --> 00:51:42.230
The same sort of criminals
that took them from me.

630
00:51:42.232 --> 00:51:44.566
But this. this is different.

631
00:51:44.568 --> 00:51:45.901
This isn't about me.

632
00:51:45.903 --> 00:51:48.670
Uh. you're telling me this why?

633
00:51:48.672 --> 00:51:52.941
This is bigger than I am.
and it's bigger than you are.

634
00:51:52.943 --> 00:51:54.175
Get out of your own way.

635
00:51:54.177 --> 00:51:58.346
Focus on what's important here.
everyone else.

636
00:51:58.347 --> 00:51:59.348
Regroup with the others.

637
00:51:59.349 --> 00:52:02.183
- And do what. exactly?
- You're loud.

638
00:52:02.185 --> 00:52:04.145
They'll listen to you
if you got something to say.

639
00:52:04.988 --> 00:52:07.522
Try to at least sound smart.

640
00:52:08.058 --> 00:52:09.058
Keep them alive.

641
00:52:09.059 --> 00:52:11.326
Keep Darkseid busy till I get back.

642
00:52:11.328 --> 00:52:12.994
Get back? From where?

643
00:52:12.996 --> 00:52:16.498
We won't win without our big gun.

644
00:52:19.268 --> 00:52:22.203
Where the hell are you going?

645
00:52:23.340 --> 00:52:24.340
Hey!

646
00:52:26.043 --> 00:52:29.311
I'm going to get Superman.

647
00:52:30.313 --> 00:52:32.981
Bruce Wayne. huh?

648
00:52:33.950 --> 00:52:37.085
Moron's crazier than I am.

649
00:53:22.765 --> 00:53:24.733
You guys ok? Good.

650
00:53:24.735 --> 00:53:27.002
Listen up

651
00:53:27.004 --> 00:53:28.770
Uh...

652
00:53:29.538 --> 00:53:31.373
ahem!

653
00:53:31.375 --> 00:53:33.341
We need to. uh...

654
00:53:33.343 --> 00:53:35.176
We need to play offense

655
00:53:35.178 --> 00:53:38.546
Instead of all coming up to bat.

656
00:53:39.281 --> 00:53:40.482
Um. what?

657
00:53:40.484 --> 00:53:44.052
I apologize. but I don't know your games.

658
00:53:44.054 --> 00:53:45.520
I think what lantern is saying

659
00:53:45.522 --> 00:53:47.722
Is that it's time for some teamwork.

660
00:53:47.724 --> 00:53:50.125
So let's pull it together.

661
00:53:50.127 --> 00:53:53.395
Yeah. baby! Clap it up!

662
00:53:56.265 --> 00:53:58.033
What's the plan. then?

663
00:53:58.034 --> 00:54:01.652
Well...
he blasts those beams out of his eyes. right?

664
00:54:01.704 --> 00:54:03.571
- It's settled. then.
- We blind him.

665
00:54:03.573 --> 00:54:08.777
That's as good a plan as any. yeah.
We follow. and we stay out of sight.

666
00:54:08.779 --> 00:54:11.813
I'll turn on the fireworks
to get his attention.

667
00:54:11.815 --> 00:54:13.782
Princess. you get in striking distance

668
00:54:13.784 --> 00:54:16.584
And stab that son of a bitch in the eyes.

669
00:54:16.586 --> 00:54:18.453
Like poor damned Oedipus.

670
00:54:18.455 --> 00:54:20.488
Yeah. what the hot Greek chick said.

671
00:54:20.490 --> 00:54:24.359
And the invasion of monsters
raining from the sky?

672
00:54:24.361 --> 00:54:25.827
What about them?

673
00:54:26.195 --> 00:54:27.695
I might be able to send them

674
00:54:27.697 --> 00:54:29.364
Back where they came from.

675
00:54:29.366 --> 00:54:31.099
Good enough for me.

676
00:54:31.101 --> 00:54:32.634
Here we go. team.

677
00:54:32.636 --> 00:54:35.070
We got this!

678
00:54:39.208 --> 00:54:40.542
"We got this"?

679
00:54:40.544 --> 00:54:41.676
That's your big battle cry?

680
00:54:41.678 --> 00:54:45.313
Don't worry about it.
smartass. Stick to the plan.

681
00:54:47.184 --> 00:54:48.184
This is awesome.

682
00:54:48.185 --> 00:54:49.584
Like that parker game in overtime.

683
00:54:49.586 --> 00:54:50.952
Where you ran the ball the last...

684
00:54:50.954 --> 00:54:53.455
All right. who are you.
and how do you know me?

685
00:54:53.456 --> 00:54:57.792
What? I'm a fan.
Everyone around here knows Victory Stone.

686
00:54:57.794 --> 00:54:59.461
I'm not that guy anymore.

687
00:54:59.463 --> 00:55:01.763
- Sure you are.
- I'm not.

688
00:55:01.765 --> 00:55:03.565
I'm a terminator. an android.

689
00:55:03.567 --> 00:55:07.135
Some kind of cyborg.
Now I'm gonna have to worry

690
00:55:07.137 --> 00:55:08.937
About operating systems and computer viruses.

691
00:55:08.939 --> 00:55:12.140
Spoiler... You won't get
to do any of that stuff

692
00:55:12.142 --> 00:55:13.741
If this guy eats the world.

693
00:55:13.742 --> 00:55:17.345
Don't you get it?
I don't have a place anywhere anymore.

694
00:55:30.493 --> 00:55:34.629
Looks to me like your place is with us.

695
00:56:11.333 --> 00:56:13.201
The parademon hives on Earth

696
00:56:13.203 --> 00:56:17.605
Were ill-equipped to process
your flesh. my prize.

697
00:56:20.510 --> 00:56:23.178
But here in my personal laboratory.

698
00:56:23.180 --> 00:56:28.366
I can splice your kryptonian genetic code
To create a new form...

699
00:56:28.918 --> 00:56:34.622
A super parademon in the service of Darkseid.

700
00:56:41.664 --> 00:56:43.231
And once we have our champion.

701
00:56:43.233 --> 00:56:49.437
We will seize the other supers
and break them as well.

702
00:56:49.439 --> 00:56:53.474
All hail Darkseid.

703
00:57:06.622 --> 00:57:08.623
Ok. remember. I'll distract him...

704
00:57:08.625 --> 00:57:10.758
- Darkseid!
- What the...

705
00:57:28.577 --> 00:57:30.011
Get him out of there.

706
00:57:30.013 --> 00:57:33.648
His showboating is
gonna ruin the entire plan.

707
00:57:33.650 --> 00:57:36.317
Oh. great. Now I'm Batman.

708
00:57:43.559 --> 00:57:45.793
- What's the big deal?
- I had him.

709
00:57:45.795 --> 00:57:48.630
- Dude. you had squat.
- We had a plan.

710
00:57:48.632 --> 00:57:51.766
Heads up. guys!

711
00:57:59.441 --> 00:58:02.310
You are a warrior. not a child.

712
00:58:02.311 --> 00:58:03.045
Act like it.

713
00:58:03.046 --> 00:58:04.712
Yes. ma'am.

714
00:58:04.714 --> 00:58:08.816
Now follow me to Victory!

715
00:58:09.551 --> 00:58:11.619
She digs me.

716
00:58:12.461 --> 00:58:13.481
Attack!

717
00:58:21.463 --> 00:58:24.715
True. the metamorphosis is painful.

718
00:58:24.767 --> 00:58:29.987
but soon... you will never
feel anything ever again.

719
00:58:31.340 --> 00:58:34.642
What? I didn't send for you.

720
00:58:39.014 --> 00:58:40.548
Let him go.

721
00:58:40.550 --> 00:58:43.751
I am impressed by your resourcefulness.
earthling.

722
00:58:43.753 --> 00:58:47.588
But once the transformative process
is set in motion.

723
00:58:47.590 --> 00:58:49.057
Nothing can stop it.

724
00:58:49.059 --> 00:58:51.392
Your friend is gone.

725
00:58:51.394 --> 00:58:55.396
With the help of the kryptonian.
I'll see to it that your world

726
00:58:55.398 --> 00:58:59.701
will be just another
that has fallen to Darkseid.

727
00:59:01.537 --> 00:59:03.638
And what if you never see it?

728
00:59:03.640 --> 00:59:05.073
You wouldn't.

729
00:59:05.075 --> 00:59:08.343
Wouldn't you?

730
00:59:13.950 --> 00:59:15.049
Welcome. my children.

731
00:59:15.051 --> 00:59:17.885
Protect your... Hunh! Unh!

732
01:00:11.874 --> 01:00:15.009
Hey. Darkseid. eat this!

733
01:00:38.200 --> 01:00:39.934
Come on. giant.

734
01:00:39.936 --> 01:00:42.069
I'm getting bored.

735
01:00:42.071 --> 01:00:45.673
This world is mine.

736
01:01:11.099 --> 01:01:14.068
One down. One to go.

737
01:01:18.740 --> 01:01:20.074
His knife was on the left side.

738
01:01:20.075 --> 01:01:21.393
Making him right-handed.

739
01:01:21.444 --> 01:01:24.344
which means the power must be... here.

740
01:04:42.377 --> 01:04:46.313
Now. Flash. take out the other eye!

741
01:04:48.917 --> 01:04:52.153
Sorry. I need this to save the world.
Thanks for your help.

742
01:05:15.210 --> 01:05:16.711
Did that work?

743
01:05:24.352 --> 01:05:28.255
Yeah. I think that worked.

744
01:05:37.733 --> 01:05:39.366
Superman!

745
01:05:39.968 --> 01:05:43.404
You need to fight
whatever they're doing to you.

746
01:05:43.406 --> 01:05:44.406
We need you. Clark.

747
01:05:44.407 --> 01:05:46.841
The world needs Clark Kent.

748
01:05:48.811 --> 01:05:50.745
Yaah!

749
01:06:04.893 --> 01:06:09.163
Both eyeballs blown out.
and he's still standing.

750
01:06:11.434 --> 01:06:13.801
What else can we do?

751
01:06:13.803 --> 01:06:16.003
Try and send him home.

752
01:06:18.006 --> 01:06:19.507
How?

753
01:06:20.342 --> 01:06:23.444
Darkseid is transferring data
to those metal cubes.

754
01:06:23.446 --> 01:06:24.845
They call them mother boxes.

755
01:06:24.847 --> 01:06:27.181
They're creating portals. boom tubes.

756
01:06:27.183 --> 01:06:29.817
I just have to speak their language.

757
01:06:29.819 --> 01:06:34.889
I didn't understand
a single word you just said.

758
01:06:38.193 --> 01:06:40.795
Connecting to network.

759
01:06:44.933 --> 01:06:47.168
Unable to connect.

760
01:06:47.170 --> 01:06:49.937
Got to get some altitude.

761
01:07:00.449 --> 01:07:02.349
Connection established.

762
01:08:04.246 --> 01:08:07.248
Get him in there.

763
01:08:18.527 --> 01:08:22.529
I'll crush you like a nut.

764
01:08:22.531 --> 01:08:24.398
Yaah!

765
01:08:28.236 --> 01:08:29.970
How dare you?

766
01:08:29.972 --> 01:08:32.172
I am Darkseid!

767
01:08:35.443 --> 01:08:38.946
I don't care.

768
01:08:40.515 --> 01:08:42.616
Kick his ass!

769
01:09:15.317 --> 01:09:19.620
- Now. kid.
- Slam the door in his face.

770
01:09:20.455 --> 01:09:22.656
Unable to connect.

771
01:09:22.658 --> 01:09:24.224
Damn it.

772
01:09:42.378 --> 01:09:43.978
Error. Error.

773
01:09:43.980 --> 01:09:47.614
The computer is not responding.

774
01:09:53.555 --> 01:09:56.256
Come on. you stupid machine.

775
01:09:56.258 --> 01:09:57.391
Work!

776
01:09:57.393 --> 01:09:59.760
Network connected.

777
01:09:59.761 --> 01:10:00.762
Yes.

778
01:10:00.763 --> 01:10:03.464
Insufficient energy.

779
01:10:03.466 --> 01:10:05.032
Shit.

780
01:10:05.134 --> 01:10:08.068
It's programmed.
But I don't have the juice to push it.

781
01:10:08.070 --> 01:10:09.403
I need a huge blast of power.

782
01:10:09.405 --> 01:10:11.538
Shouldn't be a problem.

783
01:10:18.214 --> 01:10:21.248
Shazam!

784
01:10:35.531 --> 01:10:39.500
Kryptonian. you are coming with me.

785
01:10:39.502 --> 01:10:42.703
Ohh. Like hell. I am.

786
01:10:59.788 --> 01:11:03.323
Initiating boom tube closure.

787
01:11:23.311 --> 01:11:25.279
Got you!

788
01:11:29.317 --> 01:11:33.454
Hey. you're that kid.

789
01:11:34.557 --> 01:11:36.824
Hell of a catch. man.

790
01:11:36.826 --> 01:11:37.892
Thanks.

791
01:11:38.293 --> 01:11:42.129
Don't tell them. ok?
It's none of their freaking business.

792
01:11:42.231 --> 01:11:44.581
It'll be our secret.

793
01:11:45.090 --> 01:11:48.010
I always said you had an arm like a cannon.

794
01:11:48.270 --> 01:11:51.572
Now... you totally do.

795
01:12:05.553 --> 01:12:07.354
Nice job. kid.

796
01:12:07.356 --> 01:12:09.423
Where'd Shazam go?

797
01:12:09.424 --> 01:12:11.658
He took off. said he had a hot date.

798
01:12:11.660 --> 01:12:15.429
Right. Who'd go out
with that immature hothead?

799
01:12:15.431 --> 01:12:19.533
- What about the human victims?
- I can see them.

800
01:12:19.534 --> 01:12:22.836
Let me just get this baby
to boom for me one more time.

801
01:12:27.642 --> 01:12:29.510
I got this.

802
01:12:36.217 --> 01:12:38.719
He's good for cleanup. at least.

803
01:12:38.721 --> 01:12:41.788
How do we keep Darkseid from returning?

804
01:12:41.790 --> 01:12:43.490
All those mother boxes are fried.

805
01:12:43.492 --> 01:12:46.393
Then they won't be able
to get back anytime soon.

806
01:12:46.395 --> 01:12:48.328
It's a start.

807
01:12:48.330 --> 01:12:49.730
Heads up.

808
01:12:51.299 --> 01:12:52.366
There they are.

809
01:12:52.368 --> 01:12:57.304
We should leave before
they blame us again. Ugh.

810
01:12:57.840 --> 01:13:01.241
You guys are amazing.

811
01:13:01.243 --> 01:13:03.677
What's your hurry. Flash?

812
01:13:05.180 --> 01:13:08.949
Today marks a momentous day in human history.

813
01:13:08.951 --> 01:13:12.719
In our darkest hour. these superheroes

814
01:13:12.721 --> 01:13:14.721
Donned their colorful costumes...

815
01:13:14.723 --> 01:13:16.523
- costume?
- Took to the streets...

816
01:13:16.525 --> 01:13:18.292
- this is my uniform.
- Quiet.

817
01:13:18.294 --> 01:13:19.693
Oh. now you wanna bark orders?

818
01:13:19.695 --> 01:13:22.696
After I did the heavy lifting
and pulled everyone together.

819
01:13:22.698 --> 01:13:26.233
You're referring to when you
botched my very simple directives

820
01:13:26.235 --> 01:13:28.202
And Wonder Woman led the charge?

821
01:13:28.204 --> 01:13:29.803
Cyborg showed you a video?

822
01:13:29.805 --> 01:13:31.505
He e-Mailed it to me.

823
01:13:31.507 --> 01:13:32.673
I really hate you. bats.

824
01:13:32.675 --> 01:13:35.709
I can't believe people
are no longer afraid of us.

825
01:13:35.711 --> 01:13:38.780
Or that they think we're a team.
We're not a team.

826
01:13:38.781 --> 01:13:41.682
But I am pleased to meet
some folks who get me.

827
01:13:41.684 --> 01:13:45.786
Yes.
it was good to walk among a pantheon again.

828
01:13:45.788 --> 01:13:47.287
How do you mean?

829
01:13:47.289 --> 01:13:48.855
Hades. Apollo.

830
01:13:48.857 --> 01:13:51.725
Hermes. Hephaestus. Zeus.

831
01:13:51.727 --> 01:13:54.728
Each a god in their own right.

832
01:13:54.730 --> 01:13:55.896
And me?

833
01:13:55.898 --> 01:14:00.267
I have never met anyone like you. Superman.

834
01:14:00.269 --> 01:14:01.668
God or mortal.

835
01:14:01.669 --> 01:14:02.887
<i>At this time.</i>

836
01:14:02.938 --> 01:14:04.938
<i>Is it by chance. by fate.</i>

837
01:14:04.940 --> 01:14:07.674
<i>Or are there bigger forces at work?</i>

838
01:14:07.676 --> 01:14:10.677
<i>Is our modern technological age...</i>

839
01:14:10.679 --> 01:14:11.712
I shouldn't be up here.

840
01:14:11.714 --> 01:14:15.282
- Are you kidding me?
- Of course you should. We won.

841
01:14:15.284 --> 01:14:17.884
Be proud. Your dad looks like he is.

842
01:14:17.886 --> 01:14:20.420
<i>In fact. the way of all people.</i>

843
01:14:20.422 --> 01:14:23.423
<i>working for a free and peaceful planet.</i>

844
01:14:23.425 --> 01:14:25.025
<i>As we have seen...</i>

845
01:14:25.026 --> 01:14:29.463
By the way. man.
thanks for not talking about the other thing.

846
01:14:29.465 --> 01:14:33.267
Don't sweat it.
and thanks for seeing me in here.

847
01:14:33.269 --> 01:14:35.702
- What?
- You're the bomb. Victory.

848
01:14:35.704 --> 01:14:38.839
- I know. I know.
- You keep reminding me.

849
01:14:38.841 --> 01:14:41.808
Victory. Victory.

850
01:14:41.810 --> 01:14:43.844
Victory.

851
01:14:43.846 --> 01:14:45.445
These super friends

852
01:14:45.447 --> 01:14:48.515
used their superpowers to protect us...

853
01:14:48.517 --> 01:14:50.317
and we're not friends either.

854
01:14:50.319 --> 01:14:52.586
- We let them think we're both.
- Why?

855
01:14:52.588 --> 01:14:55.422
It'll keep Gotham P.D. off my back.

856
01:14:55.424 --> 01:14:56.890
The air force off yours.

857
01:14:56.892 --> 01:14:58.525
I don't know. A team?

858
01:14:58.527 --> 01:15:01.795
I've got a lot of responsibilities.

859
01:15:01.796 --> 01:15:02.430
As do I.

860
01:15:02.431 --> 01:15:03.797
Well. I have a whole universe

861
01:15:03.799 --> 01:15:05.832
To protect. people. so there you go.

862
01:15:05.834 --> 01:15:08.001
- Come on.
- We can do it together.

863
01:15:08.003 --> 01:15:10.637
Yeah? Can you fly into space?

864
01:15:10.639 --> 01:15:11.672
I can.

865
01:15:11.673 --> 01:15:14.205
Not my point. Look. We're not friends.

866
01:15:14.206 --> 01:15:15.309
We're not a team.

867
01:15:15.310 --> 01:15:19.046
I don't agree. Hal.
I kind of liked being a part of something.

868
01:15:19.047 --> 01:15:22.349
Yeah. you would.
Listen. this was just a one-time deal. ok?

869
01:15:22.351 --> 01:15:24.918
And what if something
like this should happen again?

870
01:15:24.920 --> 01:15:27.921
- Please.
- What could possibly happen?

871
01:15:27.923 --> 01:15:30.691
That said. I am very pleased

872
01:15:30.693 --> 01:15:31.858
To introduce to you...

873
01:15:31.860 --> 01:15:33.727
Gee. I didn't even ask.

874
01:15:33.729 --> 01:15:35.696
Do you guys have a name?

875
01:15:35.698 --> 01:15:38.038
- Yes. we do.
- We do?

876
01:15:38.066 --> 01:15:40.735
That's right. You can call us...
the Super Seven.

877
01:15:41.026 --> 01:15:42.796
Please don't call us that.

878
01:15:42.938 --> 01:15:45.439
- Hera help us.
- The Super Seven?

879
01:15:45.441 --> 01:15:47.874
What? You don't like it?

880
01:17:40.054 --> 01:17:43.490
The surface dwellers have killed our king.

881
01:17:43.492 --> 01:17:48.195
This is an act of war. and they will pay.

882
01:17:49.305 --> 01:18:49.173
Do you want subtitles for any video?
-=[ ai.OpenSubtitles.com ]=-
